{"tid":981692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩同阿爸兩個食大家樂","createTime":"2019-01-14T13:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T19:45:16.000Z","uid":135177,"like":144,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5bb6fc11faa2e217d6843dbe96cf281889b302","tid":981692,"uid":135177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:12:40.000Z","msg":"好耐無面對面咁一齊食飯<br />\n望一望佢啲頭髮<br />\n發現多左幾條白頭髮<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：喂！你6幾年出世啊？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：1962年囉！死仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：原來你都差唔多6張野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咩啊！我先47歲（佢自己忍唔到偷笑左）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗚嗚<br />\n原來諗諗下爸爸都差唔多60歲<br />\n真係好想快啲讀完書出黎做野<br />\n等爸爸可以快啲退休<br />\n同佢去旅行，帶佢去啲未見過既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你地都珍惜你地既父母<br />\n多啲同佢地飲茶食飯<br />\n始終佢地心入面都係好愛你地"},{"pid":"8cd087811703746bc67118dcdfbb82b0f93c0059","tid":981692,"uid":153114,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"咩都係假 家人先係真"},{"pid":"6a333a07cb0dd7e02807e3a4eec2da259a08c048","tid":981692,"uid":78429,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"8cd087811703746bc67118dcdfbb82b0f93c0059","tid":981692,"uid":153114,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"咩都係假 家人先係真"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都有幸福家庭ok?"},{"pid":"bceff3cb11d8a3d927b95581474cdaacb0820db9","tid":981692,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知道了"},{"pid":"582f70fa64de16edcb6d8f7f21c8822ded8a5f1a","tid":981692,"uid":77171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"我個孤僻爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請佢都唔肯去旅行"},{"pid":"20fbe69982aa06e69e9328cf22e2cb7362895a80","tid":981692,"uid":224107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582f70fa64de16edcb6d8f7f21c8822ded8a5f1a","tid":981692,"uid":77171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"我個孤僻爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請佢都唔肯去旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:30:55.000Z","msg":"請食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89e6658d2cda230bb0e14be5f10d16c664f4724","tid":981692,"uid":135177,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6a333a07cb0dd7e02807e3a4eec2da259a08c048","tid":981692,"uid":78429,"like":46,"dislike":4,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"8cd087811703746bc67118dcdfbb82b0f93c0059","tid":981692,"uid":153114,"like":19,"dislike":9,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"咩都係假 家人先係真"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:16:54.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都有幸福家庭ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n好彩我爸爸係好負責任既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然佢唔有錢<br />\n但最少唔會比我同家姐挨餓"},{"pid":"23cbc8a4e8301e59e1c5c840eaca0d9c47cfccaa","tid":981692,"uid":41915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:34:54.000Z","msg":"無老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4c1c9f776987f384fe7cfd78632e3777032ad2","tid":981692,"uid":164167,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"大家樂打手"},{"pid":"bd87ac4d766bea28c9d9420dc4f11f44c5cd047e","tid":981692,"uid":56501,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"我有個老師都係6