理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 不過最後老細轉咗去第二間學校教會 electronics, 結果變咗做電子佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都搵到啖飯食下嘅"},{"pid":"552f92b69ec6deba2737a0c23e938c3b00384643","tid":981692,"uid":205674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:54:22.000Z","msg":"真係要好好珍惜。<br />\n想同枱食飯都無機會了"},{"pid":"fc47bc2540ce7b746d08aedd60b89589451bf7be","tid":981692,"uid":56501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5cd4b9f1602a92a3832fcf00b14c6bf326614d3","tid":981692,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd87ac4d766bea28c9d9420dc4f11f44c5cd047e","tid":981692,"uid":56501,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:39:06.000Z","msg":"我有個老師都係62年出世， 我由佢第一日入大學教書開始跟佢, final-year project跟佢， 畢咗業佢請我做research， 讀埋phd 結埋婚生埋細路... 跟住佢十幾年<br />\n<br />\n 十年前我忍唔住終於要離開佢 試下自己出去搵食, 嗰一刻好似要離開讓大自己嘅爸爸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 點知巴打你提一提, 原來佢都就嚟60歲都就快退休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n 時間真係過得好快有, 我有時間除咗要探下爸爸之外都要探下老師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:50:59.000Z","msg":"巴打讀咩科咁好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:54:57.000Z","msg":"我諗讀邊科好唔好都唔緊，要最緊要搵到個好老細， 會好似當我仔咁湊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fc1d67dfd9cfc97a9bab231e5b08788e825029","tid":981692,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"582f70fa64de16edcb6d8f7f21c8822ded8a5f1a","tid":981692,"uid":77171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:28:14.000Z","msg":"我個孤僻爸爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請佢都唔肯去旅行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:57:50.000Z","msg":"昆老豆，話公司抽中咗去旅行。Maximum claim幾千。唔用就冇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我上次咁樣昆咗佢地一齊去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923ee1ab689e6efbdd860c3d2a38ca83be96e1e7","tid":981692,"uid":19990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T14:03:36.000Z","msg":"我老豆係中五時因爲高血壓無返工幾年，到我大學畢業後都無返工，高血壓做唔到地盤，唔做嘢靠炒股和散工賺錢幫補，主要係老母返長工供我讀大學，我放暑假時做下兼職，<br />\n大學畢業老豆好急叫我搵野做，咩都做住先包括保安，出來做野要比三千蚊家用<br />\n畢業一年轉左幾次工就屌我唔生性，對唔住呀老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7eb915cd2600e8fd33acc40e3a67374eb4ddef2","tid":981692,"uid":83060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bab98ed046480b9f1c31ee32ded9896961985f9","tid":981692,"uid":135177,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd1b5aeb7b4e087bf5a7eafa3624e4072d081f52","tid":981692,"uid":83060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:44:48.000Z","msg":"我會從小教導子女唔可以幫襯大家樂大快活美心麥當勞呢啲食肆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔比吸管我都無咩<br />\n但岩岩凍檸茶都唔比匙我篤檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:35:08.000Z","msg":"即使無近期呢啲環保走塑呢啲事件都唔應該幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n响任何地方都係，有錢就比高價買貴嘢，無錢就比垃圾價買垃圾，最戇鳩就係去實惠大家樂大快活美心呢啲比中價買垃圾。"},{"pid":"cfbe96fdf8b645e2ddc4636acd5167dc9458b562","tid":981692,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"62年出世47歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72887d83ee1a10dc7d84d9951be1341b782cf0a","tid":981692,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfbe96fdf8b645e2ddc4636acd5167dc9458b562","tid":981692,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:41:26.000Z","msg":"62年出世47歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T19:45:16.000Z","msg":"咁都比你捉到 數學天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}